137
00:07:48,606 --> 00:07:51,289
In brief, you can say that if you borrow something,

138
00:07:51,329 --> 00:07:54,893
it's a shortcut to approved gameplay, approved market,

139
00:07:55,193 --> 00:07:56,875
maybe even a proven business model

140
00:07:56,915 --> 00:07:58,897
that you see that works for other people,

141
00:07:58,997 --> 00:08:02,001
