155
00:08:51,264 --> 00:08:55,446
Inspired by is a good way to say that you take inspiration

156
00:08:55,486 --> 00:08:56,146
from other people.

157
00:08:56,906 --> 00:09:00,047
It's typically a homage to another title,

158
00:09:00,508 --> 00:09:02,488
something that plays a bit with the original.

159
00:09:03,088 --> 00:09:06,550
And in all other aspects, it's a game totally on itself.

160
00:09:08,627 --> 00:09:12,729
