communication wise from a company standpoint and in all other aspects that are not typically gameplay related.

176
00:10:20,794 --> 00:10:27,863
Basically, making sure that you communicate the personality of the game instead of what you're actually doing.

177
00:10:32,269 --> 00:10:38,257
So if you walk into the pros and cons when you go into this market inspired by market

