00:12:24,201 --> 00:12:25,402
They want new concepts.

201
00:12:25,422 --> 00:12:28,623
They want something that stands out in the gameplay itself.

202
00:12:29,264 --> 00:12:29,464
Well.

203
00:12:30,402 --> 00:12:33,222
To be honest, this industry is a bit conservative.

204
00:12:33,803 --> 00:12:35,163
It's to be so young.

