00:47:57,436 --> 00:48:00,797
What do we think the people playing

856
00:48:00,857 --> 00:48:03,458
the game for the first time will actually experience?

857
00:48:04,198 --> 00:48:05,999
What will be their first reaction?

858
00:48:06,039 --> 00:48:07,220
What's the reaction we're after?

