00:51:16,468 --> 00:51:19,530
I have to live with her for the rest of her life,

909
00:51:20,030 --> 00:51:23,432
or my life, depending on who kicks the bucket first.

910
00:51:23,752 --> 00:51:27,034
But you have to live with your customers

911
00:51:27,375 --> 00:51:28,235
for the rest of your lives.

912
00:51:29,476 --> 00:51:31,637
And this spreads very quickly, spreads very quickly.

913
00:51:32,937 --> 00:51:35,259
Listening versus hearing on the customer side as well.

914
00:51:35,459 --> 00:51:36,959
There are many more people than you are.

915
00:51:37,460 --> 00:51:40,421
The collective knowledge of the people playing your games

916
00:51:40,721 --> 00:51:43,003
is bigger than the knowledge that you can have

917
00:51:43,043 --> 00:51:43,703
in your company.

918
00:51:44,103 --> 00:51:45,704
It's true for any company out there,

919
00:51:45,804 --> 00:51:47,805
even for Apple, with thousands of employees.

920
00:51:48,126 --> 00:51:50,667
The collective knowledge of the people using Apple's product

