00:52:40,491 --> 00:52:43,693
settings or a gameplay universe.

936
00:52:45,314 --> 00:52:47,035
People say about Europa Universalis,

937
00:52:47,875 --> 00:52:49,916
I probably don't understand this game.

938
00:52:51,017 --> 00:52:53,598
What they're saying is that I would love to have.

939
00:52:55,224 --> 00:52:56,465
a really advanced tutorial.

